    "• What are the current gaps in research about improving burnout and well-being in surgical trainees?",
    "The development of this scoping review was documented and conducted in line with the Preferred Reporting Items for Systematic Reviews and Meta-Analyses (PRISMA) Checklist.",
    "The inclusion and exclusion criteria are outlined in Table 1.",
    "Systematic reviews were excluded but separately examined to ensure all relevant studies were included.",
    "Studies included spanned the globe due to the lack of literature focusing on UK surgical training programmes."
